<li id="cite_note-9"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation book">Brown, Colin (1990). <i>Christianity &amp; Western Thought, Volume 1: From the Ancient World to the Age of Enlightenment</i>. InterVarsity Press. p.&#160;347. <a href="International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="Special_BookSources/0-8308-1752-2" title="Special:BookSources/0-8308-1752-2">0-8308-1752-2</a>.</span></span></li>
